OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will start dry with
OL,6,Fsome bright spells. However, cloud
OL,7,Fwill soon thicken from the southwest
OL,8,Fbringing some light and patchy rain
OL,9,Facross the region during the day. A
OL,10,Fmild, though breezy day with some fog
OL,11,Fpatches developing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a cloudy evening
OL,14,Fwith some drizzle and fog patches in
OL,15,Fplaces. Turning drier overnight,
OL,16,Fthough staying rather cloudy. It will
OL,17,Fbe mild, and fairly breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
