OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FTuesday will start cloudy and
OL,6,Fbreezy with patchy light rain, chiefly
OL,7,Fin the west. Brighter spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping during the day, especially
OL,9,Fin the east where it will become very
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FWednesday looks mostly dry and very
OL,14,Fmild with some sunshine, especially in
OL,15,Fthe east. Cooling down thereafter and
OL,16,Fturning more unsettled with some rain
OL,17,Fand strong winds possible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
